Test 1: Single int
add(int): 5
Result: 5

Test 2: Two ints
add(int, int): 10 + 20
Result: 30

Test 3: Three ints
add(int, int, int): 5 + 10 + 15
Result: 30

Test 4: Two strings
add(string, string): Hello + World
Result: HelloWorld

Test 5: Int and string
add(int, string): 42 + Answer
Result: 42Answer
